28:  * The Black and Vanna-Volga methods are supported.
29:  * <p>
30:  * This enum implements {@link CalculationParameter} and is used by passing it
31:  * as an argument to {@link CalculationRules}. It provides the link between the
32:  * data that the function needs and the data that is available in {@link ScenarioMarketData}.
33:  * <p>
34:  * Implementations of this interface must be immutable.
35:  */
