55:    * <p>
56:    * Parsing handles the mixed case form produced by {@link #toString()} and
57:    * the upper and lower case variants of the enum constant name.
58:    * 
59:    * @param name  the name to parse
60:    * @return the type
61:    * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the name is not known
62:    */
63:   @FromString
64:   public static FxVanillaOptionMethod of(String name) {
65:     return NAMES.parse(name);
66:   }
67: 
